Package de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.ui.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImageConverter
    ImageConverter converts images between AWT, Swing and SWT with support for Apple retina displays.
    NumberFormatter
    NumberFormatter implements basic number format operations for string stored double values.
    OpenInFileManager
    The OpenInFileManager is used to open files and folders in the file managers of the used os.
    RadioHelper
    This class implements different functionality for radio buttons in RyCON.
    ShellPositioner
    ShellPositioner implements a simple functionality to center RyCONs widgets.
    SortHelper
    This class provides static functions to sort different ArrayList for RyCON's widgets.
    StringUtils
    The StringUtils is a small set of utility methods for string operations.
    Updater
    Updater holds all the update functionality for RyCON.
